FeedPackage.Description: This package provides an OWIN middleware for user powerful authorization based on daenet’s Security Manager. By using of SecManAuthorizationMiddleware you can maintain authorization rights for applications, users, groups and their roles. SecManAuthorizationMiddleware runs after user has been successfully authenticated. It connects to Security Manager Service to get roles for the user and attach them as role claims to the existing set of claims.

FeedPackage.Description: The DevForce Application Framework makes it easy to get started with developing data-driven Rich Internet Applications (RIA) in Silverlight or WPF Desktop Applications, with Caliburn Micro as the MVVM framework and DevForce 2010 as the data access layer.
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes:
- Breaking Change: A few method signatures with references to IdeaBlade.EntityModel.Entity have been changed to reference IdeaBlade.EntityModel.IEntity in order to support Code First entities.
- New: New EntityQueryOperation.OnComplete extension methods, which attempts to cast a non-typed result to an IEnumerable<T>. - New: Out of the box debug logging for Caliburn Micro. - New: Support for Code First in addition to Model First and Database First. - New: New static method FrameworkBootstrapper.UsesFakeStore<T>() to enable fake backing store initialization in development harness and during login. - New: XML documentation files built in all configurations. - New: Includes EntityFramework 4.2 NuGet package. No longer need EntityFramework 4.1 installed to build source code. - New: Minimum required version of DevForce is now 6.1.4. - New: Release assemblies available via NuGet.
- Improved: Removed dependency on EntityManager type from FrameworkBootstrapper. - Improved: Support for initializing multiple independent fake backing stores.
FeedPackage.Title: DAF

FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes:
- New: NavigateResult class implementing reusable and customizable navigation logic. - New: Added check to prevent accidental use of an expired EntityManager.
- Improved: Added Caliburn.Micro dependency via NuGet. - Improved: Minor cosmetic fixes.
